parameters: "All I can do... is cheer on...!"
\.An insect charmer will release many bugs.
Touch and defeat all of them in the time limit.
\.Touching your ally's icon will give you
advice and the like, so... Good luck.
"Urrrgh, I don't like it... I don't like bugs..."
"Are these even bugs at this point...?"
"They may not be bugs anymore, but...
That makes them that much less scary!"
"What family are these bugs in, even?
Where could their native habitat even be?!"
"Yes, I must sketch this bizarre bug!
"Right now, we can't lose at any cost!
The sketch can wait until later!"
You can't lose to the gross bugs, meow!!"
"I hate bugs, woof!! I wanna go home, meow!!"
"Big sis Sara... Urgh... I can only cheer you on...
"I'll do my best for big sis Sara, meowww...
My heart's gonna give in, woofff..."
"At last, a monster shows up, meow! Scary, woof!!"
"There's no way we can lose, meow!
I vowed to protect big sis Sara, woof!!"
